text: Michael Tse (born 13 January 1964) is a Hong Kong rower. He competed in the men's single sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Hong Kong male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Hong Kong Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Rowers at the 1994 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Hong Kong
